{"questionId":"358f18bc","correctAnswer":"1728","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Use the vertex formula","content":"For $f(x)=ax^{2}+bx+c$, the vertex is at $x=-\\tfrac{b}{2a}=-\\tfrac{-48}{2}=24$."},{"title":"Substitute to find $f(24)$","content":"Substitute: $$f(24)=24^{2}-48(24)+2304=576-1152+2304=1728.$$"},{"title":"State the minimum","content":"The answer is <strong>1728</strong>."}]}